10 SUMMARY
1111 This bill clarifies that an investigation team of the Department of Health and Human
1122 Services may share information with the superintendent of a school administrative unit, the
1133 chief administrator of a private school or a public school not in a school administrative unit
1144 when there is an indicated or substantiated finding of out-of-home child abuse or neglect
1155 against an employee of or a student registered in that school administrative unit, public
1166 school not in a school administrative unit or private school.
